{"tid":1942131,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【齊心抗疫】狂人也有善良一面 摩連奴低調向老人家送暖","createTime":"2020-03-25T00:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T12:44:02.000Z","uid":41343,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eb663bd6c01112643c5bb0115537f9ce20836ead","tid":1942131,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T00:58:32.000Z","msg":"熱刺領隊摩連奴素有「狂人」的稱號，隨著英國因武漢肺炎疫情肆虐、英超停擺，作為領隊的摩連奴放假主動去做義工，低調展示其善良一面。<br />\n<br />\n英國每日郵報報道，摩連奴在熱刺附近的慈善機構合作，準備一些食品及其他生活必需品，交給社區中的家人老及弱勢社群。摩連奴更在該慈善機構的twitter，利用自己的名氣向外界作出呼籲：「我是來幫助他們的，當然你亦可以捐贈食物、金錢或成為義工。」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，在這個疫情嚴重的時刻，熱刺守將艾達韋列特已向醫院捐贈平板電腦，另一守將維頓漢更公關呼籲，任何不遵守距離令的人應該罰款，並將款項轉給醫護機構。"},{"pid":"208fa40bc9acd25265f75451d51aabfaa125765a","tid":1942131,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:00:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200324/AZKPYOP3OEYKUE5MUFHG3GSR5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200324%2FAZKPYOP3OEYKUE5MUFHG3GSR5Y%2F&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=78633a00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200324%2FAZKPYOP3OEYKUE5MUFHG3GSR5Y%2F&h=5604ef3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200324/AZKPYOP3OEYKUE5MUFHG3GSR5Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/Hwwb43cwhy2tLOq3fYG8NtyeZeY=/346x522/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/GGNJEAXSN6KOKVFNKCIQDFJBXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FHwwb43cwhy2tLOq3fYG8NtyeZeY%3D%2F346x522%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FGGNJEAXSN6KOKVFNKCIQDFJBXM.jpg&h=d5043c54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/Nq_UVmQjnm2ZpP2kj-X3l6MNrCg=/346x259/arc-photo